    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sleeveless knee-length vestments worn by cardinals, bishops, and certain other high-ranking ecclesiastics.The color of the garment indicates rank.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
